1
00:02:07,080 --> 00:02:10,680
After all, they are inferior Daoist sects from the mortal realm.

2
00:02:11,640 --> 00:02:13,500
I've had enough playing with you.

3
00:02:14,800 --> 00:02:16,880
Die.

4
00:02:39,520 --> 00:02:41,000
Sister Gesang!

5
00:02:43,520 --> 00:02:45,000
With this little skill,

6
00:02:45,040 --> 00:02:46,840
you dare to run wild in Tushan.

7
00:02:59,480 --> 00:03:00,360
Got it.

8
00:03:03,400 --> 00:03:04,640
My blood.

9
00:03:05,680 --> 00:03:07,280
How does it taste?

10
00:03:12,920 --> 00:03:14,080
What's going on?

11
00:03:15,640 --> 00:03:17,079
What did you do to me?

12
00:03:21,320 --> 00:03:22,640
In my blood,

13
00:03:23,200 --> 00:03:25,000
various spores are cultivated.

14
00:03:26,040 --> 00:03:26,960
My blood.

15
00:03:27,800 --> 00:03:29,440
are my weapons.

16
00:03:30,800 --> 00:03:32,079
Right now, they

17
00:03:32,920 --> 00:03:34,840
should be inside your body,

18
00:03:35,480 --> 00:03:37,200
multiplying wildly.

19
00:03:42,000 --> 00:03:42,720
You're bleeding a lot.

20
00:03:42,720 --> 00:03:43,720
Let me bandage it for you.

21
00:03:43,720 --> 00:03:44,920
Don't touch my blood.

22
00:03:48,400 --> 00:03:49,120
So back then,

23
00:03:49,120 --> 00:03:50,920
she didn't let me touch her blood

24
00:03:51,320 --> 00:03:52,250
because of this.

25
00:04:56,120 --> 00:04:59,000
I can't believe it's a brat like you.

26
00:05:01,440 --> 00:05:02,970
I am a disciple of Qingxuan.

27
00:05:10,200 --> 00:05:12,520
No one can kill me in Tushan.

28
00:05:14,120 --> 00:05:15,320
Just you wait.

29
00:05:24,960 --> 00:05:25,480
Sister Gesang.

30
00:05:25,480 --> 00:05:26,040
Sister.

31
00:05:26,040 --> 00:05:27,100
Don't come closer.

32
00:05:30,800 --> 00:05:32,040
If you touch my blood,

33
00:05:32,680 --> 00:05:33,800
I can't save you.

34
00:05:34,320 --> 00:05:35,280
Sister Gesang.

35
00:05:35,520 --> 00:05:37,080
But you're so badly injured.

36
00:05:37,080 --> 00:05:38,240
What should we do?

37
00:05:38,920 --> 00:05:40,320
Hurry and get some water.

38
00:05:41,360 --> 00:05:43,240
Water, water, water.

39
00:05:43,480 --> 00:05:44,120
Hurry.

40
00:05:56,880 --> 00:05:58,080
Gods.

41
00:06:05,640 --> 00:06:06,500
High Immortal.

42
00:06:07,680 --> 00:06:08,680
How could this be?

43
00:06:11,440 --> 00:06:12,680
If Qingxuan hadn't shown

44
00:06:12,680 --> 00:06:15,010
the Hong Sword to the Heavenly Venerable,

45
00:06:15,120 --> 00:06:16,560
the Heavenly Realm really wouldn't know

46
00:06:16,560 --> 00:06:19,490
that you had secretly descended to the mortal realm.

47
00:06:20,320 --> 00:06:22,880
Today, I've come specifically to apprehend you.

48
00:06:22,880 --> 00:06:24,010
Do you plead guilty?

49
00:06:27,080 --> 00:06:27,880
Guilty?

50
00:06:30,640 --> 00:06:31,440
Guilty?

51
00:06:34,240 --> 00:06:35,840
What crime have I committed?

52
00:06:39,520 --> 00:06:40,960
Why is the Hong Sword

53
00:06:41,440 --> 00:06:43,360
used to help people ascend,

54
00:06:44,800 --> 00:06:47,060
while I am only used to punish immortals?

55
00:06:48,640 --> 00:06:50,370
For tens of thousands of years,

56
00:06:50,840 --> 00:06:53,040
how many immortal roots have I severed?

57
00:06:53,880 --> 00:06:55,940
How much resentment have I absorbed?

58
00:07:04,440 --> 00:07:05,720
I no longer want

59
00:07:06,520 --> 00:07:07,480
to be that

60
00:07:07,800 --> 00:07:09,800
ominous object feared by all.

61
00:07:11,880 --> 00:07:12,740
High Immortal,

62
00:07:13,800 --> 00:07:15,660
if you really want to take me away,

63
00:07:17,200 --> 00:07:19,080
just kill me right here.

64
00:07:19,800 --> 00:07:21,060
All things in the world

65
00:07:21,320 --> 00:07:22,980
born between heaven and earth

66
00:07:23,240 --> 00:07:24,840
merely have their own roles.

67
00:07:25,440 --> 00:07:27,280
Whether ominous or not,

68
00:07:28,640 --> 00:07:30,400
whether to kill you or not,

69
00:07:31,720 --> 00:07:33,250
is not a choice for you or me.

70
00:07:33,800 --> 00:07:34,440
Let's go.

71
00:07:35,040 --> 00:07:37,280
The Heavenly Venerable will decide.

72
00:07:50,600 --> 00:07:51,440
Yes.

73
00:07:56,480 --> 00:07:58,409
Return Qingxuan's immortal root.

74
00:08:37,559 --> 00:08:38,360
Qingxuan.

75
00:09:14,200 --> 00:09:15,400
Greetings, High God.

76
00:09:16,280 --> 00:09:18,610
How many years have you been cultivating?

77
00:09:18,840 --> 00:09:20,040
Over a hundred years.

78
00:09:20,720 --> 00:09:22,480
To have the opportunity to come to Sanshanliu

79
00:09:22,480 --> 00:09:24,400
in just a short century,

80
00:09:25,240 --> 00:09:26,170
it shows that you

81
00:09:26,600 --> 00:09:28,000
are quite gifted.

82
00:09:28,920 --> 00:09:30,200
Sanshanliu?

83
00:09:33,880 --> 00:09:34,880
I am not talented.

84
00:09:35,080 --> 00:09:36,480
I had an epiphany in Qingqiu,

85
00:09:36,480 --> 00:09:38,320
and ascended here in a single thought.

86
00:09:38,320 --> 00:09:39,040
I don't know

87
00:09:40,040 --> 00:09:41,720
the name of this precious land.

88
00:09:41,720 --> 00:09:42,680
In this world,

89
00:09:43,800 --> 00:09:45,930
all those who cultivate immortality,

90
00:09:46,440 --> 00:09:47,320
whether human

91
00:09:48,440 --> 00:09:49,120
or demon,

92
00:09:50,000 --> 00:09:51,880
if they have the chance to attain the Dao,

93
00:09:51,880 --> 00:09:53,880
they will ascend here in their minds.

94
00:09:53,880 --> 00:09:55,340
Through that Dharma gate,

95
00:09:56,520 --> 00:09:58,360
they can reach the Nine Heavens

96
00:09:58,800 --> 00:10:00,260
in the body of an immortal.

97
00:10:02,320 --> 00:10:03,450
Thank you, High God.

98
00:10:05,520 --> 00:10:07,920
But how

99
00:10:08,160 --> 00:10:09,880
do I pass through this Dharma gate?

100
00:10:09,880 --> 00:10:10,920
And where is

101
00:10:11,280 --> 00:10:12,520
this Dharma gate?

102
00:10:13,720 --> 00:10:15,850
Wait for me by the table under the tree.

103
00:10:16,320 --> 00:10:17,450
Thank you, High God.

104
00:10:32,080 --> 00:10:33,540
To understand the destiny

105
00:10:33,560 --> 00:10:34,800
and know the nature.

106
00:10:35,520 --> 00:10:36,800
Cultivation here,

107
00:10:38,040 --> 00:10:39,120
when life ends,

108
00:10:39,800 --> 00:10:41,530
all must enter reincarnation.

109
00:10:41,840 --> 00:10:42,800
The heavenly dao

110
00:10:43,200 --> 00:10:44,400
is also like this.

111
00:10:56,520 --> 00:10:57,520
Drink this tea

112
00:10:58,520 --> 00:11:00,520
to manifest your worldly emotions.

113
00:11:01,280 --> 00:11:03,540
I will sever them with the Rainbow Sword.

114
00:11:03,640 --> 00:11:04,770
Sever your thoughts

115
00:11:05,520 --> 00:11:06,720
and leave them here.

116
00:11:07,720 --> 00:11:10,380
Then you can pass through that gate with purity.

117
00:11:11,800 --> 00:11:12,930
Thank you, High God.

118
00:11:15,920 --> 00:11:16,920
But High God,

119
00:11:17,360 --> 00:11:20,280
if my emotions are severed after drinking this tea...

120
00:11:20,280 --> 00:11:21,940
Will the memories of the world

121
00:11:22,040 --> 00:11:23,040
still exist?

122
00:11:23,400 --> 00:11:25,060
Memories will not disappear.

123
00:11:25,440 --> 00:11:26,840
It's just that your willpower

124
00:11:26,840 --> 00:11:28,640
will become clearer and firmer.

125
00:11:29,320 --> 00:11:31,050
Your perspective on all things

126
00:11:31,280 --> 00:11:33,480
will be completely different from now.

127
00:11:35,400 --> 00:11:37,000
Thank you for your guidance.

128
00:12:28,800 --> 00:12:29,600
Thank you.

129
00:12:30,200 --> 00:12:31,080
Go.

130
00:13:07,000 --> 00:13:08,920
Cultivating as the Qingqiu Fox Clan

131
00:13:08,920 --> 00:13:11,120
has blocked your true power, hasn't it?

132
00:13:11,600 --> 00:13:14,260
I heard you possess extraordinary magic power.

133
00:13:14,680 --> 00:13:15,880
But looking at it now,

134
00:13:16,200 --> 00:13:17,640
it's nothing special.

135
00:13:25,480 --> 00:13:27,810
Jinwang's demonic aura has disappeared.

136
00:13:31,920 --> 00:13:32,920
Golden Immortal.

137
00:13:33,720 --> 00:13:35,360
Just give in to me,

138
00:13:35,920 --> 00:13:37,980
so you'll suffer less physical pain.

139
00:13:39,040 --> 00:13:39,840
My Lady.

140
00:13:43,960 --> 00:13:44,760
My Lady.

141
00:13:46,880 --> 00:13:47,680
I beg you.

142
00:13:47,880 --> 00:13:49,160
Save me.

143
00:13:49,160 --> 00:13:50,520
Give me Chilan Bi'an.

144
00:13:53,680 --> 00:13:55,840
What makes you think I will save you?

145
00:13:59,480 --> 00:14:01,640
I have served you for centuries

146
00:14:01,920 --> 00:14:03,250
with absolute loyalty.

147
00:14:04,040 --> 00:14:05,080
Please.

148
00:14:05,080 --> 00:14:06,120
Save me.

149
00:14:07,600 --> 00:14:09,880
I will do anything for you from now on.

150
00:14:25,000 --> 00:14:26,560
Thank you, My Lady.

151
00:14:35,280 --> 00:14:35,920
My Lady,

152
00:14:36,360 --> 00:14:37,800
what are you doing?

153
00:14:48,440 --> 00:14:51,170
Didn't you promise to help me become an immortal?

154
00:15:11,320 --> 00:15:12,720
Sorry you had to see that.

155
00:15:13,680 --> 00:15:15,200
I'll ask you one last time.

156
00:15:16,600 --> 00:15:18,400
Do you want to cultivate with me?

157
00:15:18,880 --> 00:15:19,880
If I am to

158
00:15:20,400 --> 00:15:21,730
lose my life here today,

159
00:15:22,520 --> 00:15:23,680
it is my fate.

160
00:15:51,200 --> 00:15:52,400
Sorry to trouble you.

161
00:15:52,520 --> 00:15:53,600
Long time no see.

162
00:15:53,600 --> 00:15:54,130
High God.

163
00:15:54,720 --> 00:15:55,650
Long time no see.

164
00:15:56,920 --> 00:15:58,920
The High God delivering you with the Hong Sword

165
00:15:58,920 --> 00:15:59,920
is his mercy.

166
00:16:01,720 --> 00:16:02,580
Immortal root.

167
00:16:03,000 --> 00:16:04,000
It is merely

168
00:16:04,000 --> 00:16:06,930
the compassion of the primal energy attached to him.

169
00:17:12,160 --> 00:17:12,319
Ping Jieqiang.
